\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Trust is about being able to see past the current situation and into God\'92s final solution which is your salvation. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\ls8\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
